PHILLIS: Hello. It’s good to meet you. My name is Phillis Wheatley… I don’t normally talk to strangers, but it’s my first time in London and I could do with some company. 

I’ve heard that today, something strange is going on with the time-zones. I’m in 1773. But there are rumours that people from 2022 - and many different times - are roaming about the streets today. Is that true? Are you … are you … one of the one’s from the future? Your clothes suggest that that would be correct, because I’ve never seen anything like it…

